"Zhihui Xiaxiang" 2021 China International Rail Transit and Equipment Manufacturing Industry Talent Summit opened - Rolling News - Hunan Daily - Huasheng Online Hunan Daily December 10 (All Media Reporter Zhou Zhiheng) 9, " Zhihui Xiaxiang" 2021 China International Rail Transit and Equipment Manufacturing Industry Talent Summit opened in Zhuzhou. China International Rail Transportation and Equipment Manufacturing Industry Talent Summit opened in Zhuzhou. Wang Cheng, member of the Standing Committee of the Provincial Party Committee and Minister of the Organization Department of the Provincial Party Committee, attended the opening ceremony and made a speech. Wang Cheng pointed out that the talent summit is an important initiative to implement the central talent work conference and the spirit of the 12th Party Congress of the province, which shows the sincere sincerity of Hunan in attaching importance to talents, thirsting for talents and using talents well. Hunan has a fine tradition of talent recognition, talent love and respect, a broad platform to help the development of talent, and environmental conditions to achieve a good life. In recent years, Hunan has been deeply implementing the strategy of talent-led development, taking Furong Talent Action Plan as the traction, building up a whole chain of talent attraction, cultivation, retention and use, and becoming a fertile ground for talent growth and achievement, a hot spot for innovation and entrepreneurship, and a pleasant place to live and work. At present, Hunan is fully implementing the strategic positioning and mission of "three high and four new", and will further open the door to attract talents, introduce better policies, concentrate more resources and create better conditions for talents' innovation and entrepreneurship, expecting outstanding talents from all walks of life to pool their wisdom and strength for the high-quality development of Hunan. At the event, Changsha, Zhuzhou, Xiangtan pavilion and Hunan Pilot Free Trade Zone pavilion were set up. The Provincial Department of Science and Technology, the Provincial Department of Industry and Information Technology and the Provincial Department of Human Resources and Social Security released the list of key demands for science and technology innovation in advanced manufacturing-related industries, the directory of intelligent manufacturing industry talent demand, and the directory of intelligent manufacturing industry youth talent demand for postdoctoral mobile stations. Forty-eight large enterprises such as China CNR, Zoomlion and Yuanda Technology solicited talents on site, and nearly 1,000 fresh graduates of relevant majors and social talents participated in talent project matching.
